{
    "_comment": "Phase 1 – layer-aware budget, monotone-increasing profile.",
    "_comment_detail": [
        "Hypothesis: deeper layers need more blocks for cross-segment retrieval.",
        "24 layers, mean=16 blocks (total = 24*16 = 384, preserved for fair comparison).",
        "Profile: layers 0-5 = 8, layers 6-11 = 12, layers 12-17 = 20, layers 18-23 = 24.",
        "Mean = (6*8 + 6*12 + 6*20 + 6*24) / 24 = (48+72+120+144)/24 = 384/24 = 16."
    ],
    "attention_bias": false,
    "bos_token_id": 1,
    "eos_token_id": 2,
    "fuse_cross_entropy": true,
    "fuse_norm": true,
